    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/b77de475af107ff2902250466f1e7254.avif?t=1764593152\" width=616 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fae &amp; Fauna</strong> is an open world creature collecting role-playing game combining the very best elements of the genre! Expand your base, complete quests, craft new gear and head out on exciting adventures with your pet companions, called Faeons. Take on the role as a research student at the Saltwick Academy, where not all is what it seems... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/57b804ac6240e45a40c099773bf52bbe.avif?t=1764593152\" width=616 height=79 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/32c55161c933b7225160ceb6b0f9c479.poster.avif?t=1764593152\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/32c55161c933b7225160ceb6b0f9c479.webm?t=1764593152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight together! </strong>Assemble your own team of adorable Faeons, that each have their own special powers as you traverse the islands of Saltwick. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/ff2a6b19b7c3176c39bc0434a220a400.avif?t=1764593152\" width=616 height=79 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/46b63e3f0c88434e3348a03c3a3d1ae2.poster.avif?t=1764593152\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/46b63e3f0c88434e3348a03c3a3d1ae2.webm?t=1764593152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Collect &amp; Craft!</strong> As you adventure you will find plenty of materials that can be used in alchemy to create new pet companions, craft new gear, make tasty food or furniture for your home.<br><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/1e155bd9a3aeb15d72336961986ce33d.avif?t=1764593152\" width=616 height=79 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/ead9351ebf1bd46c8694c08edefe7333.poster.avif?t=1764593152\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/ead9351ebf1bd46c8694c08edefe7333.webm?t=1764593152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Decorate &amp; Expand!</strong> Design and decorate your home to reflect your perfect haven. Customize your home with magical furniture, whimsical knicknacks, and charming decorations you’ve picked up along the way. Expand your base to provide a sanctuary for your growing collection of pets, offering them cozy nests, play areas, and more.<strong> </strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/06955a92af5913ca3155a7b0559e31e0.avif?t=1764593152\" width=616 height=79 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/4e86ccde7351fabb8164f6dc8de8045d.poster.avif?t=1764593152\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/4e86ccde7351fabb8164f6dc8de8045d.webm?t=1764593152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Bond!</strong> Care for your pets! Play with them, feed them or simply head out into the world together! Every moment you spend together will increase your bond with one another. Raise your most favorite friend in the world - and cuddle to your heart's content!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/ec615125403e5cfa2f0d34ddb03b62f6.avif?t=1764593152\" width=616 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/0b5dcbd331dead6a032578088822cc4b.poster.avif?t=1764593152\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/0b5dcbd331dead6a032578088822cc4b.webm?t=1764593152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find friendship, or even love?</strong> Connect with  captivating characters, where something special could blossom. Create your own story, and explore the world of Lunora!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/b1cf05a2e5e44dea191f3a5c512544f2.poster.avif?t=1764593152\" width=600 height=54 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363200/extras/b1cf05a2e5e44dea191f3a5c512544f2.webm?t=1764593152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
